Shirkadda Panasonic Corporation (Panasonicku Kabushiki-gaisha), oo horay loo yiqiin Matsushita Electric Industrial Co., Ltd. (Matsushita Denki Sangy≈ç Kabushiki-gaisha), waa shirkad Japan oo caalami ah oo qalabka elektarooniga ah oo xarunteedu tahay Kadoma, Osaka, Japan . [1]
Shirkadda waxaa la aasaasay sannadkii 1918 iyada oo soo saarey saldhigyo saldhigyo shidaal ah waxayna kor u qaadeen inay noqdaan mid ka mid ah soo saarayaasha ugu waawayn Japan ee ku shaqeeya Sony, Hitachi, Toshiba iyo Canon Inc. Marka lagu daro qalabka elektarooniga ah, waxay bixisaa alaab aan elektaroonik ahayn iyo adeegyo sida guriga adeegyada dayactirka. Panasonic waa shirkadda afaraad ee dunida ugu weyn dunida oo dhan iyadoo la adeegsanayo qaybta suuqyada ee 2012. [2]
Panasonic wuxuu leeyahay liiska hoose ee shirkadda Tokyo Stock Exchange wuxuuna ka kooban yahay Nikkei 225 iyo TOPIX indices. Waxay leedahay liis heer sare ah ee Nagoya Stock Exchange.
